    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rigid airships consisting of a covered and trussed frame supported by compartments or cells filled with gas; developed in Germany around 1900.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
